    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索对您的绘画做出反应的世界的第一幕。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/3a9484c66474b4f6a5f250f271b6af50.poster.avif?t=1739520130\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/3a9484c66474b4f6a5f250f271b6af50.webm?t=1739520130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/3a9484c66474b4f6a5f250f271b6af50.mp4?t=1739520130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心地探索一个危险而令人心碎的世界。探索你可以画什么来填补这个世界，解决谜题，修复损坏的东西。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁并升级独特的能力。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/7d223f9644d427d1c41f17814f1cfc68.poster.avif?t=1739520130\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/7d223f9644d427d1c41f17814f1cfc68.webm?t=1739520130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/7d223f9644d427d1c41f17814f1cfc68.mp4?t=1739520130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现强大的文物，赋予你新的能力。水晶可以引导人们对新大陆进行更大的探索。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >向未知世界中的公民学习。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/c36e628a5e8f7725e367e4472d2aac37.poster.avif?t=1739520130\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/c36e628a5e8f7725e367e4472d2aac37.webm?t=1739520130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/c36e628a5e8f7725e367e4472d2aac37.mp4?t=1739520130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与隐藏的角色建立关系，帮助他们完成任务，与他们进行交易，并了解你的旅程的重要信息。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >找到隐藏的东西并充分探索地图。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/6219ed4361363a2989f4ec6946c1ccf5.poster.avif?t=1739520130\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/6219ed4361363a2989f4ec6946c1ccf5.webm?t=1739520130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293560/extras/6219ed4361363a2989f4ec6946c1ccf5.mp4?t=1739520130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入研究相互关联的地图，直到找到完成演示的出路。重新探索过去的区域，解锁每项能力和升级，结识所有角色，并了解未来谜团的答案。</p>",
